parameters:
Moo! I finally found you! I won't give that child to you
guys!

\SE[2] Ahh... This child is also me, but... it feels like
they were born too early... \SE[3] If things continue like
this, you... will die.

\SE[4]What will you do? Do you want me to help you? \SE[3]Or
do you want to just die like this?

\SE[2]They still can't speak. \!\SE[4]But if they don't say
something... I won't understand. \!\SE[2]Even just a
little... Do they know any words?

\SE[2]Do you want to live, or do you want to die? It seems
like you still don't know... \SE[32]But... do you have
someone you want to see?

\SE[34]In that case... there's no choice but to live.
\!\SE[3]But with a body that's less than that of a child,
they'll die soon.... \!\SE[16]So let's make them take on a
grown-up form for just a little while.

Ah...! I've become a lovely lady! I think I look very
beautiful...!

Well then, shall we go meet your 'mom'...? I will... take
you there.
